<title>CEUNAK TLUNG KO SEH CH408</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Muihnak chung a um-mi sinah, Nangmah ceunak tlung ko seh, A kan
 Khamhtu Jesuh thawngin, Khamhnak kha an hmuh khawh lai.

[C1]
   Maw Bawipa, ceunak run pe ko, Rili ral khua zakip ah, Na dawtnak le
   vel-ngeihnak cu, man pek loin an hmuh lai.

[V2]
 Zan khuamui ngaih-chiatnak chungin, A tlaumi thlarau khamh tuah. A
 caan zong kha a dih zau lai, Rianrang in i tim ko tuah.

[C2]
   Maw Bawipa, ceunak run pe ko, Rili ral khua zakip ah, Na dawtnak le
   vel-ngeihnak cu, man pek loin an hmuh lai.

[V3]
 Nangmah nih na zultu hna cu, &quot;Thawngthabia kha chim ko u, Nanmah sinah
 ka um zungzal,&quot; tiah bia kha na kan kam cang.

[C3]
   Maw Bawipa, ceunak run pe ko, Rili ral khua zakip ah, Na dawtnak le
   vel-ngeihnak cu, man pek loin an hmuh lai.

[V4]
 Maw kal lengmang Gospel teinak, Rili le khua zakip ah, Muihnak vialte
 ceu cang ko seh, A caan kha a luan hlan ah.

[C4]
   Maw Bawipa, ceunak run pe ko, Rili ral khua zakip ah, Na dawtnak le
   vel-ngeihnak cu, man pek loin an hmuh lai.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>